{
  "id": "69b087829b53ce976edc3153",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:謙遜の文化",
  "created": 1773176795,
  "updated": 1773176839,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69b087829b53ce976edc3153",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:謙遜の文化",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176795,
      "updated": 1773176795
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087da000000000047daf7",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176795,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047daf8",
      "text": "やっほー！今日は「謙遜の文化」ってテーマでゆるっとトークしてくよ〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047daf9",
      "text": "なんかさ、日本って「いやいや自分なんて全然です」みたいなやつ多くない？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047dafa",
      "text": "ゲームでいうと、SSR引いてるのに「いや爆死でした」って言うタイプ。あれ何なん？って思うときあるんだよねｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047dafb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047dafc",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047dafd",
      "text": "そうですね……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047dafe",
      "text": "日本では昔から、自分を低くして相手を立てることが、礼儀のひとつとして大切にされてきたのだと思います。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047daff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db00",
      "text": "たとえば誰かに褒められたとき、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db01",
      "text": "「ありがとうございます」と受け取るよりも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db02",
      "text": "「いえいえ、まだまだでございます」とお答えする。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db03",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db04",
      "text": "それはまるで、春の草花が風に身をゆだねるような、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db05",
      "text": "控えめでやさしい姿勢の表れなのかもしれませんね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db07",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db08",
      "text": "概念的には「謙遜」は社会的摩擦を下げるコミュニケーション技術と言える。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db09",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db0a",
      "text": "自分の能力を強く主張すると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db0b",
      "text": " 他者との競争が激化する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db0c",
      "text": " 嫉妬や対立が生じる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db0e",
      "text": "そこで自己評価を意図的に低く見せることで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db0f",
      "text": "集団の安定性を保つプロトコルとして機能している。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db10",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db11",
      "text": "社会心理学でも似た概念がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db12",
      "text": "いわゆる modesty bias（謙遜バイアス）。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db13",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Modesty",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db14",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db15",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db16",
      "text": "うおー急に難しいワード来たｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db17",
      "text": "つまりさ、人間関係のバグ回避パッチってこと？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db18",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db19",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db1a",
      "text": "近い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db1c",
      "text": "自己アピールが強すぎると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db1d",
      "text": "コミュニティ内の感情リソースが枯渇する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db1e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db1f",
      "text": "謙遜はそれを防ぐ社会的ロードバランサーの役割を持つ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db21",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db22",
      "text": "「ロードバランサー」という言葉は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db23",
      "text": "人と人との心の重さを、そっと均してくれるもののように聞こえますね。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db24",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db25",
      "text": "けれども……",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db26",
      "text": "あまりにも自分を低く言いすぎると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db27",
      "text": "その方の努力や才能が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db28",
      "text": "まるで霧の中に隠れてしまうようで、少し寂しい気もいたします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db2a",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db2b",
      "text": "あーわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db2c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db2d",
      "text": "なんかさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db2e",
      "text": "ガチで上手い人ほど「いや全然ですよ」って言う現象あるじゃん。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db30",
      "text": "でも初心者からすると",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db31",
      "text": "「いやいやいやいや！めっちゃ強いじゃん！！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db32",
      "text": "ってなるんだよねｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db33",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db34",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db35",
      "text": "それは興味深い観察だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db36",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db37",
      "text": "日本ではしばしば",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db38",
      "text": "能力が高い人ほど謙遜する傾向がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db39",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db3a",
      "text": "理由の一つは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db3b",
      "text": "「能力が高い＝自覚している欠点も多い」から。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db3d",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db3e",
      "text": "メタ認知が高い人ほど自己評価が控えめになる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db3f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db40",
      "text": "心理学では ダニング＝クルーガー効果とも関連する。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db41",
      "text": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dunning%E2%80%93Kruger_effect",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db42",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db43",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db44",
      "text": "あ、それ聞いたことある！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db46",
      "text": "弱い人ほど「自分強い！」って言って、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db47",
      "text": "強い人ほど「まだまだ…」ってなるやつでしょ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db48",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db49",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db4a",
      "text": "概ねその理解で問題ない。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db4b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db4c",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db4d",
      "text": "そう考えると、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db4e",
      "text": "謙遜というものは、ただの遠慮ではなく、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db4f",
      "text": "自分の未熟さを静かに見つめる心なのかもしれませんね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db51",
      "text": "本を読んでおりますと、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db52",
      "text": "昔の武士や学者も、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db53",
      "text": "自分の学びを誇るより、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db54",
      "text": "「まだ道の途中でございます」と語ることが多いように感じます。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db55",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db56",
      "text": "その姿には、どこか凛とした美しさがあります。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db58",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db59",
      "text": "なるほどな〜。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db5a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db5b",
      "text": "でもさ、海外だと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db5c",
      "text": "「自分すごいです！」って言うの普通だったりするよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db5d",
      "text": "あれ文化の違いって感じする。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db5f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db60",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db62",
      "text": "文化比較では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db63",
      "text": " 日本：collectivism（集団主義）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db64",
      "text": " 欧米：individualism（個人主義）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db65",
      "text": "の傾向がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db66",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db67",
      "text": "個人主義では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db68",
      "text": "自己アピール＝能力の証明。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db6a",
      "text": "集団主義では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db6b",
      "text": "謙遜＝協調性の証明。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db6c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db6d",
      "text": "評価基準が異なる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db6e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db6f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db70",
      "text": "文化とは、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db71",
      "text": "人々が長い年月をかけて紡いできた「心の作法」のようなものですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db72",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db73",
      "text": "ですから、どちらが良い悪いというよりも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db74",
      "text": "それぞれの土地で育った礼儀なのでしょう。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db75",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db76",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db77",
      "text": "まとめるとこんな感じ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db78",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db79",
      "text": " 謙遜＝人間関係を平和にするスキル",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db7a",
      "text": " 強い人ほど控えめになること多い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db7b",
      "text": " 国によって「正しい態度」が違う",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db7c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db7d",
      "text": "なんか…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db7e",
      "text": "日本のコミュニティ用マナーって感じだね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db7f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db80",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db81",
      "text": "その整理は妥当。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db82",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db83",
      "text": "ただし一点補足。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db85",
      "text": "謙遜は有効だが、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db86",
      "text": "過度になると自己評価の低下や機会損失を招く。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db87",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db88",
      "text": "バランスが重要。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db89",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db8a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db8b",
      "text": "ええ……。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db8c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db8d",
      "text": "花も、あまりに深くうつむけば、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db8e",
      "text": "太陽の光を受け取れませんものね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db8f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db90",
      "text": "控えめでありながら、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db91",
      "text": "ときには自分の努力を大切に認める。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db92",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db93",
      "text": "そのような心のあり方が、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db94",
      "text": "いちばん美しいのかもしれません。（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db96",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db97",
      "text": "おお〜今日の名言出たｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db99",
      "text": "じゃあ今日の結論！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db9b",
      "text": "「謙遜は日本の神スキル。でも使いすぎはナーフされる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db9d",
      "text": "ってことで！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087db000000000047db9f",
      "text": "はい、今日のゆる鼎談おしまい〜！ 🎮✨",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176796,
      "updated": 1773176796
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087f5000000000047dba0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176821,
      "updated": 1773176821
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087f5000000000047dba1",
      "text": "#2026-03-11",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176821,
      "updated": 1773176839
    },
    {
      "id": "69b087f7000000000047dba2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773176823,
      "updated": 1773176823
    }
  ]
}